  · exact conj_univariate_u
      M hMul hInv F_U R hFU j k h0j hjk hZeroInit hDelta hCurrent hSubst hFactor hTailZero
  · intro v
    exact solution_u_product
      M hMul hInv F_U R hFU j k h0j hjk hZeroInit hDelta hCurrent hSubst hFactor hTailZero v
  · exact eval_solution_u F_U R j h0j k hjk
  · exact succ_solution_u F_U R j h0j k hjk

